Genre: eLearning | Figure Drawing | 25 min 54 secs | Beginner - Intermediate
Uploaded in Feb 0, 2015 by 2boweb



In this video lesson expert draftsman and painter Danny Galieote will review some of the fundamentals of figure drawing. First you will learn how to analyze the rhythms within the figure. Then you will see how to apply the anatomical landmarks within your rhythmic lay-in of the pose. And finally you will apply fundamentals of structure to give your drawings a solid rhythmic and harmonious result.
